{
  "texts": [
    "Incorporating diversity broadens the explored solution space, leading to a more accurate identification of worst-case scenarios, thereby improving the GA's effectiveness in real-time system performance analysis.",
    "The observed maximum execution times surpass those in other categories with only execution time as fitness function.",
    "The lower standard deviation for the GA using both execution time and diversity as fitness functions, compared to using only execution time, suggests a more thorough search space exploration.",
    "When guided solely by execution time, the GA might not fully explore the search space, leading to variability in average execution times across iterations.",
    "Conversely, incorporating diversity encourages systematic exploration, resulting in more consistent outcomes."
  ]
}